title: Electric Luna maker Kinetic Green raises US$25 mn for aggressive growth in its e2W, e3W biz
description: Kinetic Green has received a $25 million investment from Greater Pacific Capital as part of its Series A fundraise. This company aims to scale production, expand dealership networks, and accelerate research and development in the EV sector.
